What does the following program print?

```cpp
#include <iostream>

int main()
{
    int x = 10;
    int y = 3;
    std::cout << x / y << '\n';
    std::cout << x % y << '\n';
    std::cout << x - (x / y) * y << '\n';
    return 0;
}
```

